OL,6,FA community that was the centre of
OL,7,Flarge scale riots last year is the
OL,8,Fsubject of a new action plan to turn
OL,9,Fthe area around, which includes
OL,10,Fbuilding better relationships between
OL,11,Fresidents and the police.
OL,13,FMore than 1,200 local people were
OL,14,Fconsulted to create a Community Plan
OL,15,Ffor Ely and Caerau, which was
OL,16,Fpublished on Tuesday.
