OL,3,CAction plan to turn around community
OL,4,Cone year on from large scale riots
OL,6,FThe plan ` created with the
OL,7,Finvolvement of a grassroots community
OL,8,Forganisation ` sets out actions with
OL,9,Fthe aim of making "a significant
OL,10,Fpositive difference in the coming
OL,11,Fyears."
OL,13,FActions include introducing a series
OL,14,Fof programmes for residents and young
OL,15,Fpeople in the Ely and Caerau area of
OL,16,FCardiff to help boost their trust in
OL,17,Fthe police, delivering more
OL,18,Fopportunities for jobs and training
OL,19,Ffor young people in the area, and the
OL,20,Fstrengthening of mental health support
OL,21,Ffor teenagers.
