OL,3,CAction plan to turn around community
OL,4,Cone year on from large scale riots
OL,6,FThe plan also includes developing
OL,7,Fextra-curricular activities on offer,
OL,8,Ftackling anti-social behaviour
OL,9,F"hotspots" and improving green spaces
OL,10,Fin the area.
OL,12,FResidents consulted talked about a
OL,13,F"sense of pride and resilience within
OL,14,Fthe community," and said they have
OL,15,Fdisliked the way the community is
OL,16,Foften portrayed as "troubled" and
OL,17,Fwithout a sense of hope.
