OL,3,CAction plan to turn around community
OL,4,Cone year on from large scale riots
OL,6,FThe plan said it aims to draw on "the
OL,7,Fexisting strengths" of Ely and Caerau
OL,8,Fas a place, "rather than simply
OL,9,Fidentifying problems."
OL,11,FIt comes as the community was left
OL,12,Freeling after the sudden deaths of
OL,13,FHarvey Evans and Kyrees Sullivan last
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,Fwere riding on an electric bike when
OL,17,Fthey were involved in a collision in
OL,18,Fthe Ely area of the city.
OL,20,FFollowing their deaths, large scale
OL,21,Fdisorder broke out in the area.
