OL,3,CAction plan to turn around community
OL,4,Cone year on from large scale riots
OL,6,FLocal resident and ACE volunteer
OL,7,FLeyton Smith said: "I'm so excited for
OL,8,Fthese plans about everybody coming
OL,9,Ftogether - local people and charities
OL,10,Fcoming together as one, putting their
OL,11,Fminds together and to move forward
OL,12,Fwith positive directions.
OL,14,F"There's a lot on the table and I
OL,15,Fthink if we achieve half of that it
OL,16,Fwill be something but we aim to
OL,17,Fachieve it all."
