OL,6,FHe added: "We've had some stigma in
OL,7,Fthis area for many years but we're
OL,8,Fgoing to knock that on the head and
OL,9,Fwe're going to get rid of that. We're
OL,10,Fall working together - local youth
OL,11,Fservices, faiths, churches, schools,
OL,12,Fall independent businesses, all coming
OL,13,Ftogether to get these youngsters
OL,14,Fsomething when they leave school.
OL,16,F"Something is put in place - they're
OL,17,Fnot forgotten about, we can not be
OL,18,Fforgotten about any more, we need
OL,19,Factions and that's what this steering
OL,20,Fgroup is all about."
